| 4 | `/cpl:test-plan` | sonnet | `requirements.md`, `architecture.md` | `test_plan.md` |
| 5 | `/cpl:gen` | haiku | `tasks.md`, `architecture.md`, `ui_spec.md` | код + `impl_notes.md` |
| 5s | `/cpl:gen-server` | haiku | `tasks.md`, `architecture.md`, `api_contracts.md` | код + `impl_notes.md` |
| 6 | `/cpl:gen-tests` | haiku | `tasks.md`, `test_plan.md` | тесты |
| 7 | `/cpl:code-review` | sonnet | diff + `architecture.md` | `review.md` |
| 8 | `/cpl:debug` | sonnet | логи/stacktrace + `debug.md` | `debug.md` + код-фикс |
